    "templateData": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n    <head>\n        <title>CT HCC Screening</title>\n        <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.identifier\" content=\"T1425224589795\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.title\" content=\"CT HCC Screening\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.description\" content=\"CT for HCC Screening\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.type\" content=\"IMAGE_REPORT_TEMPLATE\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.language\" content=\"en\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.publisher\" content=\"Radiological Society of North America (RSNA)\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.rights\" content=\"May be used freely, subject to license agreement\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.license\" content=\"http://www.radreport.org/license.pdf\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.date\" content=\"2015-03-01\" />\n        <meta name=\"dcterms.creator\" content=\"Parag P. Tolat\" />\n        <script type=\"text/xml\">\n            <template_attributes>\n                <coded_content></coded_content>\n            </template_attributes>\n        </script>\n    </head>\n    <body>\n        <section id=\"procedureInformation\" class=\"level1\" data-section-name=\"Procedure Information\">\n            <header class=\"level1\">\n                Procedure Information\n            </header>\n            <p>\n                <label for=\"procedureInformationText\"></label>\n                <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"procedureInformationText\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\"></textarea>\n            </p>\n            <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239703\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Technique\">\n                <header class=\"level2\">\n                    Technique\n                </header>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719\">IV contrast type</label>\n                    <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"ALERT\" value=\"Visipaque-320\">\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719_0\" value=\"Omnipaque-350\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719\">Omnipaque-350</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719_1\" value=\"Visipaque-320\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719\" selected=\"\">Visipaque-320</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719_2\" value=\"Isovue-370\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239719\">Isovue-370</option>\n                    </select>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"NUMBER_1425225239726\">IV Contrast Dose</label>\n                    <span>\n                        <input type=\"number\" step=\"1.0\" data-field-units=\"mL\" id=\"NUMBER_1425225239726\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"NUMBER\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"125\" />\n                        mL\n                    </span>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727\">Oral Contrast</label>\n                    <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"ALERT\" value=\"Water\">\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727_0\" value=\"None\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727\">None</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727_1\" value=\"Water\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727\" selected=\"\">Water</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727_2\" value=\"Volumen\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727\">Volumen</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727_3\" value=\"Positive (iodinated)\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239727\">Positive (iodinated)</option>\n                    </select>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733\">Technical Comments</label>\n                    <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Dual-phase with equilibrium\">\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733_0\" value=\"Standard single phase\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733\">Standard single phase</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733_1\" value=\"Dual-phase\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733\">Dual-phase</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733_2\" value=\"Dual-phase with equilibrium\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733\" selected=\"\">Dual-phase with equilibrium</option>\n                        <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733_3\" value=\"Dual-phase, dual-energy\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239733\">Dual-phase, dual-energy</option>\n                    </select>\n                </p>\n            </section>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"clinicalInformation\" class=\"level1\" data-section-name=\"Clinical Information\">\n            <header class=\"level1\">\n                Clinical Information\n            </header>\n            <p>\n                <label for=\"clinicalInformationText\"></label>\n                <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"clinicalInformationText\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\"></textarea>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"comparisons\" class=\"level1\" data-section-name=\"Comparison\">\n            <header class=\"level1\">\n                Comparison\n            </header>\n            <p>\n                <label for=\"comparisonsText\"></label>\n                <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"comparisonsText\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\"></textarea>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"findings\" class=\"level1\" data-section-name=\"Findings\">\n            <header class=\"level1\">\n                Findings\n            </header>\n            <p>\n                <label for=\"findingsText\"></label>\n                <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"findingsText\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\"></textarea>\n            </p>\n            <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239738\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"HEPATOBILIARY SYSTEM\">\n                <header class=\"level2\">\n                    HEPATOBILIARY SYSTEM\n                </header>\n                <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239765\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Liver Morphology:\">\n                    <header class=\"level2\">\n                        Liver Morphology:\n                    </header>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239767\"></label>\n                        <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239767\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Cirrhosis evidenced by heterogeneous appearance, surface nodularity, and/or hypertrophy of the left/caudate lobes\">\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239767_0\" value=\"Normal\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239767\">Normal</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239767_1\" value=\"Cirrhosis evidenced by heterogeneous appearance, surface nodularity, and/or hypertrophy of the left/caudate lobes\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239767\" selected=\"\">Cirrhosis evidenced by heterogeneous appearance, surface nodularity, and/or hypertrophy of the left/caudate lobes</option>\n                        </select>\n                    </p>\n                </section>\n                <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239772\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Portal Hypertension:\">\n                    <header class=\"level2\">\n                        Portal Hypertension:\n                    </header>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239773\">Described the presence/absence of portal hypertension. If present, described the portosystemic varices.</label>\n                        <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239773\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\"></textarea>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775\">Spleen</label>\n                        <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Splenomegaly\">\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775_0\" value=\"Normal\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775\">Normal</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775_1\" value=\"Splenomegaly\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775\" selected=\"\">Splenomegaly</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775_2\" value=\"\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239775\"></option>\n                        </select>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"NUMBER_1425225239779\">Spleen Size</label>\n                        <span>\n                            <input type=\"number\" step=\"0.1\" data-field-units=\"cm\" id=\"NUMBER_1425225239779\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"NUMBER\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\" />\n                            cm\n                        </span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780\">Ascites</label>\n                        <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Mild\">\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780_0\" value=\"None\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780\">None</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780_1\" value=\"Mild\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780\" selected=\"\">Mild</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780_2\" value=\"Moderate\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780\">Moderate</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780_3\" value=\"Severe\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239780\">Severe</option>\n                        </select>\n                    </p>\n                </section>\n                <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239785\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Focal Liver Lesions:\">\n                    <header class=\"level2\">\n                        Focal Liver Lesions:\n                    </header>\n                    <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239817\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"   Lesions compatible with hepatocellular carcinoma by OPTN class 5 criteria:\">\n                        <header class=\"level2\">\n                             Lesions compatible with hepatocellular carcinoma by OPTN class 5 criteria:\n                        </header>\n                    </section>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239836\"></label>\n                        <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239836\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"None or describe lesion(s)\"></textarea>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"NUMBER_1425225239818\">Lesion number:</label>\n                        <span>\n                            <input type=\"number\" step=\"1.0\" data-field-units=\"\" id=\"NUMBER_1425225239818\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"NUMBER\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"1\" />\n                        </span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"NUMBER_1425225239819\">Lesion size:</label>\n                        <span>\n                            <input type=\"number\" step=\"0.1\" data-field-units=\"cm\" id=\"NUMBER_1425225239819\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"NUMBER\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\" />\n                            cm\n                        </span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"NUMBER_1425225239821\">Lesion segment location:</label>\n                        <span>\n                            <input type=\"number\" step=\"1.0\" data-field-units=\"\" id=\"NUMBER_1425225239821\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"NUMBER\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\" />\n                        </span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239822\">Hypervascularity:</label>\n                        <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239822\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Yes\">\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239822_0\" value=\"Yes\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239822\" selected=\"\">Yes</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239822_1\" value=\"No\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239822\">No</option>\n                        </select>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239825\">Washout:</label>\n                        <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239825\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"No\">\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239825_0\" value=\"Yes\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239825\">Yes</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239825_1\" value=\"No\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239825\" selected=\"\">No</option>\n                        </select>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239829\">Capsule/pseudocapsule:</label>\n                        <select multiple=\"multiple\" id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239829\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"SELECTION_LIST\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Yes\">\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239829_0\" value=\"Yes\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239829\" selected=\"\">Yes</option>\n                            <option id=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239829_1\" value=\"No\" name=\"SELECTION_LIST_1425225239829\">No</option>\n                        </select>\n                    </p>\n                    <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239834\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Indeterminate liver lesions:\">\n                        <header class=\"level2\">\n                            Indeterminate liver lesions:\n                        </header>\n                        <p>\n                            <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239835\"></label>\n                            <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239835\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"None.\"></textarea>\n                        </p>\n                    </section>\n                    <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239837\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Benign liver lesions:\">\n                        <header class=\"level2\">\n                            Benign liver lesions:\n                        </header>\n                        <p>\n                            <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239838\"></label>\n                            <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239838\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"None.\"></textarea>\n                        </p>\n                    </section>\n                </section>\n                <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239793\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Hepatic vasculature:\">\n                    <header class=\"level2\">\n                        Hepatic vasculature:\n                    </header>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239794\">Portal and hepatic veins:</label>\n                        <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239794\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Normally patent.\"></textarea>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239795\">Arterial anatomy:</label>\n                        <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239795\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Normal (type 1).\"></textarea>\n                    </p>\n                </section>\n                <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239796\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"Gallbladder and bile ducts:\">\n                    <header class=\"level2\">\n                        Gallbladder and bile ducts:\n                    </header>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239797\">Gallbladder:</label>\n                        <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239797\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Gallbladder in situ. No gallbladder wall thickening or pericholecystic fluid.\"></textarea>\n                    </p>\n                    <p>\n                        <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239798\">Bile ducts:</label>\n                        <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239798\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"No intra-or extrahepatic biliary dilatation.\"></textarea>\n                    </p>\n                </section>\n            </section>\n            <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239799\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"RETROPERITONEUM\">\n                <header class=\"level2\">\n                    RETROPERITONEUM\n                </header>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239800\">Pancreas:</label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239800\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Normal\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239801\">Adrenals glands:</label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239801\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Normal\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239802\">Kidneys:</label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239802\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Normal.\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239803\">Lymph nodes:</label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239803\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"No lymphadenopathy in the abdomen or pelvis.\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n            </section>\n            <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239804\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"GASTROINTESTINAL\">\n                <header class=\"level2\">\n                    GASTROINTESTINAL\n                </header>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239806\"></label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239806\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Imaged bowel and mesentery are normal.\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n            </section>\n            <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239807\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"LOWER CHEST\">\n                <header class=\"level2\">\n                    LOWER CHEST\n                </header>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239809\">Heart:</label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239809\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Normal size.\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239810\">Lungs:</label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239810\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"Lung bases are clear.\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239811\">Fluid:</label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239811\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"No pleural or pericardial effusions.\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n            </section>\n            <section id=\"SECTION_HEADER_1425225239812\" class=\"level2\" data-section-name=\"BONES\">\n                <header class=\"level2\">\n                    BONES\n                </header>\n                <p>\n                    <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239813\"></label>\n                    <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239813\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"No significant lesion.\"></textarea>\n                </p>\n            </section>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"impression\" class=\"level1\" data-section-name=\"Impression\">\n            <header class=\"level1\">\n                Impression\n            </header>\n            <p>\n                <label for=\"impressionText\"></label>\n                <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"impressionText\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"\"></textarea>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239814\">OPTN class 5 criteria:</label>\n                <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239814\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\" The following OPTN class 5 criteria are used to determine if liver lesions are compatible with hepatocellular carcinoma by imaging, as follows:  OPTN Class 5A - Must meet ALL criteria:    1. Nodule measuring between 1 and 1.9 cm.    2. Increased contrast enhancement on late arterial phase (&quot;hypervascularity&quot;), relative to hepatic parenchyma.    3. BOTH &quot;washout&quot; on later contrast phase AND delayed peripheral rim enhancement (capsule/pseudocapsule).  OPTN Class 5A-g - Must meet ALL criteria:    1. Nodule measuring between 1 and 1.9 cm.    2. Increased contrast enhancement on late arterial phase (hypervascularity relative to hepatic parenchyma).    3. Growth (maximum diameter) by 50% or more on serial MR/CT obtained at least 6 months apart. Growth criteria does not apply to previously ablated lesions.  OPTN Class 5B - Must meet ALL criteria:    1. Nodule measuring between 2 and 5 cm.    2. Increased contrast enhancement on late arterial phase (&quot;hypervascularity&quot;), relative to hepatic parenchyma.    3. One of the following:        a. &quot;Washout&quot; on portal venous/delayed phase.        b. Delayed peripheral rim enhancement (capsule/pseudocapsule).        c. Growth (maximum diameter) by 50% or more on serial MR/CT obtained at least 6 months apart. Growth criteria does not apply to previously ablated lesions        d. Biopsy proven.  http://optn.transplant.hrsa.gov/resources/by-organ/liver-intestine/\"></textarea>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <label for=\"TEXT_1425225239815\">Milan Criteria:</label>\n                <textarea rows=\"3\" cols=\"100\" id=\"TEXT_1425225239815\" name=\"\" data-field-type=\"TEXT\" title=\"\" data-field-completion-action=\"NONE\" value=\"   -  one lesion smaller than 5 cm     -  up to 3 lesions smaller than 3 cm    -  no extrahepatic manifestations     -  no vascular invasion\"></textarea>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n    </body>\n</html>\n",
